Package: review
Title: Tidy Relational Algebra for Semantic Review
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Language: en-GB
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Daniel", 
           family = "Antal", 
           email = "daniel.antal@dataobservatory.eu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7513-6760"))
Description: Provides a tidy relational algebra for iterative semantic
    review of tabular data. The package creates reviewable claims from
    ordinary data frames, allocates successive review rounds, records
    provenance for each review, and finalises reviewed values while
    preserving review history. It supports reproducible review workflows
    that remain compatible with ordinary data frames and metadata packages
    such as 'dataset'.
